41:56.433 --> 41:59.102
* Are you lonely *

41:59.144 --> 42:01.187
* Are you missing
your one and only *

42:01.229 --> 42:03.815
* Starting to write the end
of your story *

42:03.857 --> 42:06.026
* You're alive... *

42:06.067 --> 42:08.445
* Are you breathin' *

42:08.486 --> 42:10.780
